      "content": "Resumo: Deterministic board state composed from official captured components.\nÉpico: Assumption - pending planning ID\nHistória: Assumption - pending planning ID\nUser stories: Assumption - pending planning ID\nRequisitos: Assumption - pending planning ID\nRegras: Sidebar uses shadcn official source; Kanban uses Dice UI official source; both are connected Pencil refs.\nEstado / gatilho: default - open the Product roadmap board.\nCritérios: Sidebar and three Kanban columns are visible; source component refs remain inspectable.\nAnterior / próximo: Product entry → trello-menu, trello-dialog, or trello-board-empty."
