      "width": 1180,
      "height": 300,
      "content": "Resumo: Card editing state with title, description, ownership, and save controls.\nÉpico: Assumption - pending planning ID\nHistória: Assumption - pending planning ID\nUser stories: Assumption - pending planning ID\nRequisitos: Assumption - pending planning ID\nRegras: Cancel preserves the prior card; save applies valid changes and returns to the board.\nEstado / gatilho: dialog - open card details from the board or actions menu.\nCritérios: Context remains visible; editable fields are clear; save and cancel are explicit.\nAnterior / próximo: trello-board or trello-menu → trello-board or trello-card-moved."
