      "content": "Resumo: Destructive confirmation requires explicit intent before permanently deleting a card.\nÉpico: Assumption - pending planning ID\nHistória: Assumption - pending planning ID\nUser stories: Assumption - pending planning ID\nRequisitos: Assumption - pending planning ID\nRegras: Only authorized members can delete; deletion is irreversible; exact confirmation text is required.\nEstado / gatilho: confirmation - choose Delete from trello-menu.\nCritérios: Target card is named; impact is explicit; cancel is safe; destructive action is visually distinct.\nAnterior / próximo: trello-menu → trello-board on cancel or trello-board after deletion."
