      "height": 300,
      "content": "Resumo: Successful card movement is reflected in the destination column with non-blocking feedback.\nÉpico: Assumption - pending planning ID\nHistória: Assumption - pending planning ID\nUser stories: Assumption - pending planning ID\nRequisitos: Assumption - pending planning ID\nRegras: A card occupies exactly one column; feedback identifies the destination; board order is preserved.\nEstado / gatilho: success feedback - drop or move a card into In progress.\nCritérios: Destination is visible; moved card is identifiable; confirmation does not block subsequent work.\nAnterior / próximo: trello-board or trello-dialog → trello-board after feedback expires."
