      "width": 1280,
      "height": 300,
      "content": "Resumo: Official shadcn dashboard-01 reference captured from the supplied registry command.\nÉpico: Assumption - pending planning ID\nHistória: Assumption - pending planning ID\nUser stories: Assumption - pending planning ID\nRequisitos: Replicate the official dashboard-01 layout and visual hierarchy in Pen.dev.\nRegras: Preserve the sidebar, header, metric cards, chart, data table, full-height content, and canonical shadcn styling.\nEstado / gatilho: dashboard reference - npx shadcn add dashboard-01.\nCritérios: Screen matches the captured reference; no top-level overlaps; all layers follow Name (id).\nAnterior / próximo: trello-clone board flows → Screen UZQ0E."
