      "content": "Resumo: Dashboard base materialized from the official shadcn dashboard-01 block.\nÉpico: Assumption - pending planning ID\nHistória: Assumption - pending planning ID\nUser stories: Navigate work, inspect the data table, and invoke global or row-level actions.\nRequisitos: Sidebar and data table remain visible in a coherent full-height shell.\nRegras: dashboard-01 is the visual base; captured origins remain local to this .pen.\nEstado / gatilho: default - open the dashboard.\nCritérios: Sidebar, header, metric cards, chart, and table are visible without top-level overlap.\nAnterior / próximo: Entry → command menu, dropdown menu, or dialog state."
    },
